## Objective
The objective of this lab was to create tags and asssign them to resource groups in the Azure portal. This enabled tagging to be enforced and applied by a policy. I can configure a resource lock and test the resourcde to ensure the locks are functioning correctly.
## What I did
1. I Created and assign tags via the Azure portal.
2. I Enforced tagging via an Azure Policy.
3. I Applied tagging via an Azure Policy.
4. I Configured and test resource locks.

